OL,3,CMy Community Series: The market where
OL,4,Cprices are not based on profit
OL,6,FEvery Friday, 10am. That's when locals
OL,7,Fin one of Guernsey's parishes come
OL,8,Ftogether at a non-profit community
OL,9,Fmarket to not only provide fresh
OL,10,Fproduce but also an important lifeline
OL,11,Ffor their neighbours.
OL,13,FStarting with just one stall a decade
OL,14,Fago, the North Community Market in the
OL,15,FVale has grown substantially and
OL,16,Faround 15 stallholders now take part
OL,17,Fregularly.
