OL,3,CMy Community Series: The market where
OL,4,Cprices are not based on profit
OL,6,FIslanders can buy a range of items
OL,7,Ffrom fresh fruit and vegetables to
OL,8,Fhandmade stuffed toys and birthday
OL,9,Fcards.
OL,11,FHowever, many just go for the
OL,12,Fopportunity to socialise with people
OL,13,Fthey otherwise would not see with the
OL,14,Fchance to catch-up over a coffee and
OL,15,Ftake part in a raffle.
