OL,3,CMy Community Series: The market where
OL,4,Cprices are not based on profit
OL,6,FJanet Dereham helped set it up and
OL,7,Fsays: "As we all get older, we do
OL,8,Fless. The market gives people an
OL,9,Fopportunity to meet new people and
OL,10,Fmake friends, so it's just a brilliant
OL,11,Fidea and I hope more parishes take it
OL,12,Fup."
OL,14,FThe market is not for profit with all
OL,15,Fthe proceeds put towards renting the
OL,16,FDouzaine room and the costs of keeping
OL,17,Fit going.
