OL,3,CMy Community Series: The market where
OL,4,Cprices are not based on profit
OL,6,FOrganiser Sarah Breton adds: "It's a
OL,7,Fmeeting point, it's social and
OL,8,Fregular. People have a chance to pick
OL,9,Fup things they are using for events
OL,10,Fsuch as Christmas cards. However, the
OL,11,Fmain thing is that it's like a coffee
OL,12,Fmorning which brings huge amounts of
OL,13,Fhelp and support for people who need
OL,14,Fit most."
OL,16,FJanet and Sarah were interviewed as
OL,17,Fpart of ITV Channel's 'My Community
OL,18,FSeries' which celebrates the
OL,19,Fimportance of coming together - it can
OL,20,Fbe a cookery class, a sports session,
OL,21,Ffriends meeting up and much more.
